<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>GAP Investor | Inversión en EE. UU.</title>
   
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
   
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500&family=Outfit:wght@700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

    <style>
        h1, h2 { font-family: 'Outfit', sans-serif; }
        p, span, button, a { font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; }

        /* Animación personalizada de brillo para el botón */
        @keyframes shimmer {
            0% { transform: translateX(-100%); }
            100% { transform: translateX(100%); }
        }
        .animate-shimmer {
            animation: shimmer 2s infinite;
        }

        /* Suavizado de scroll */
        html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-[#03000a] antialiased">

    <section class="relative min-h-screen w-full flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
       
        <div class="absolute top-[-10%] left-[-5%] w-[30rem] md:w-[50rem] h-[30rem] md:h-[50rem] bg-purple-900/20 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-[-10%] right-[-5%] w-[25rem] md:w-[45rem] h-[25rem] md:h-[45rem] bg-indigo-950/30 rounded-full blur-[120px] pointer-events-none"></div>

        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,#80808012_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,#80808012_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:40px_40px] [mask-image:radial-gradient(ellipse_60%_50%_at_50%_50%,#000_70%,transparent_100%)] pointer-events-none"></div>

        <div class="container relative z-10 mx-auto px-6 text-center">
           
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-purple-500/30 bg-purple-500/5 mb-8 animate-fade-in transition-all hover:bg-purple-500/10 cursor-default">
                <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
                    <span class="animate-ping absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-purple-400 opacity-75"></span>
                    <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-purple-500"></span>
                </span>
                <span class="text-[10px] md:text-xs font-medium tracking-[0.2em] text-purple-200 uppercase">Equity de Clase Mundial</span>
            </div>

            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl lg:text-8xl font-extrabold text-white leading-[1.05] tracking-tight mb-8">
                El futuro de tu capital es <br>
                <span class="bg-gradient-to-b from-purple-200 via-purple-400 to-purple-600 bg-clip-text text-transparent">
                    GAP Investor
                </span>
            </h1>

            <p class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-base md:text-xl text-slate-400 font-light leading-relaxed mb-12">
                Domina el mercado de valores de EE. UU. con un vehículo de inversión de renta variable diseñado para maximizar rendimientos a largo plazo. Inversión inteligente, exposición global y solidez patrimonial.
            </p>

            <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-6">
                <button class="relative group overflow-hidden px-10 py-4 bg-purple-600 rounded-full transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-purple-500 hover:shadow-[0_0_40px_8px_rgba(147,51,234,0.3)] active:scale-95 shadow-lg shadow-purple-900/20">
                    <div class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-white/20 to-transparent -translate-x-full animate-shimmer"></div>
                   
                    <span class="relative text-white font-bold text-lg flex items-center gap-2">
                        Abrir mi cuenta
                        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M5 12h14m-7-7 7 7-7 7"/></svg>
                    </span>
                </button>
               
                <button class="text-white font-medium text-lg hover:text-purple-300 transition-colors flex items-center gap-2 group">
                    Explorar portafolio
                    <span class="group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform">→</span>
                </button>
            </div>

            <div class="mt-24 flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center gap-x-12 gap-y-6 opacity-30 grayscale transition-all duration-700 hover:grayscale-0 hover:opacity-80">
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                    <span class="text-white font-bold tracking-tighter text-xl md:text-2xl">NASDAQ</span>
                    <span class="text-[10px] text-purple-400 uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Tech Leaders</span>
                </div>
                <div class="h-8 w-[1px] bg-slate-800 hidden md:block"></div>
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                    <span class="text-white font-bold tracking-tighter text-xl md:text-2xl">NYSE</span>
                    <span class="text-[10px] text-purple-400 uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Institutional</span>
                </div>
                <div class="h-8 w-[1px] bg-slate-800 hidden md:block"></div>
                <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
                    <span class="text-white font-bold tracking-tighter text-xl md:text-2xl">S&P 500</span>
                    <span class="text-[10px] text-purple-400 uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Market Standard</span>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>
    </section>

</body>
</html>
